original: Ljungdahl, Folke August, ingenjör, Nyibro, f. 6/1/11 i Nybro av dir. Sture L. o. Ida Isacsson. G. 44. Barn: Agneta f. 45, Pia 47. Ingiex. i Örebro 31. Res. t. USA 33, Tyskl. o. Frankr. 37. Verkst. dir. i A-B Nybro Wellkartong fr. 37. Led. av styr. i A-B Sture Ljungdahl & Co. i Nybro, Skand. Bank. Nybrokont., Nybro stads el.- o. vattenverk led. av Kalm. 1. södra landsting sed. 43. Hob-bies: idr., foto o. trädgrsköts. Riksidr:-förb. Gm m. emalj, SkidlöpGm m. £1.
translated: Ljungdahl, Folke August, engineer, Nybro, born on January 6, 1911 in Nybro to director Sture L. and Ida Isacsson. Married in 1944. Children: Agneta, born in 1945, and Pia, born in 1947. Employed in Örebro until 1931. Moved to the US in 1933, and worked in Germany and France from 1937. Became the managing director of A-B Nybro Wellkartong in 1937. Also served on the board of directors of A-B Sture Ljungdahl & Co. in Nybro and Skand. Bank. Also held positions in Nybrokont., Nybro city's electricity and water works, and was a member of the Kalm. 1st Southern County Council since 1943. Hobbies include sports, photography, and gardening. Member of the National Sports Association. Married with an unknown partner. Skied with a partner.

employments.name: Nybro city's electricity and water works
